<p><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:verdana;">The NY Journal of Books also gave a thoughtful review, for those wishing to learn more:&nbsp;<a href="http://sendy.gentlemachineproductions.com/l/cMLktUNrVTNtBIo83rD4Ow/LGpSol9biHKY1r892LJhlhcg/3bNqIqy5FnIPu2SzbnJuPQ" target="_blank">Go here to view.</a></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:verdana;">Furthermore, for those interested in reading the introduction of the book, please go here:<br />
<a href="http://sendy.gentlemachineproductions.com/l/cMLktUNrVTNtBIo83rD4Ow/3xW3dCbuD4vJFhYhZO6XuA/3bNqIqy5FnIPu2SzbnJuPQ" target="_blank">http://www.thenewhumanrightsmovement.com/why-this-book/</a><br />
<br />
