<p><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:verdana;">&ldquo;Peter Joseph is one of the great visionaries of our time. If there&#39;s a beautiful future&mdash;and I think there will be&mdash;then his fingerprints will be all over it.&rdquo;-&nbsp;<i>Marianne Williamson</i>,&nbsp;<i>#1 New York Times bestselling author</i></span></span></p>

